Original: Ugh... You're going to take... that
request? I posted it up high, where I
hoped no one would see it...
[Page]

wants someone to bring him back a
[Color:5]moth egg[Color:0].
[Page]

naturally. Now... a word, please. You
needn't try so hard on this one...
[Page]
I shall... I shall await your...
swift... return.
